.git/
.gitignore

# The committed generated module (root go.mod + recursive .go) is a REVIEWED derived artifact, NOT a
# generation/proof input: exclude it from the ordinary Buildx context so the pristine `generated-module`
# layer is derived ONLY from certified .v + dune + plugin/sink + witnesses (never the committed bytes).
# (The staged-index pre-commit reads the committed bytes host-side from the exported git index, not Buildx.)
/go.mod
**/*.go

# Local build output + transient control/crash residue (never a build input)
/.fido/
**/*.fido-tmp-v1
/fido
*.test
*.out
vendor/
.env

# Rocq artifacts (reproducible from .v sources inside the image)
*.glob
*.vo
*.vok
*.vos
*.vio
.coq-native/

# Editor / OS noise
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo
